      What this publication is, why it exists, and what it will and will not do.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="sg-layout">

    <aside class="sg-nav" aria-label="Page sections">
      <a href="#what-we-are">What we are</a>
      <a href="#why-we-exist">Why we exist</a>
      <a href="#what-we-stand-for">What we stand for</a>
      <a href="#what-we-will-not-do">What we will not do</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </aside>

    <div class="article-body">

      <h2 id="what-we-are">What We Are</h2>
      {% for p in aboutContent.whatWeAre %}<p>{{ p }}</p>{% endfor %}

      <h2 id="why-we-exist">Why We Exist</h2>
      {% for p in aboutContent.whyWeExist %}<p>{{ p }}</p>{% endfor %}

      <h2 id="what-we-stand-for">What We Stand For</h2>
